law CarSale
authority private
enacted 2025-03-01

vocabulary
    verb deliver: deliver
    verb delivery: deliver
    verb pay: pay

parties
    Seller: Alice Corp
    Buyer: Bob

objects
    Car: movable
    Price: money

article 1 Exchange
    obligation Seller must deliver Car to Buyer.
    claim Seller may demand pay of Price from Buyer.
    procedure Closing:
        Seller delivers Car to Buyer.
        Buyer pays Price to Seller.
